###  Displaying a pending visual state during the Transition

You can use the ` isPending ` boolean value returned by ` useTransition ` to
indicate to the user that a Transition is in progress. For example, the tab
button can have a special “pending” visual state:



    function TabButton({ children, isActive, onClick }) {  


      const [isPending, startTransition] = useTransition();  


      // ...  


      if (isPending) {  


        return <b className="pending">{children}</b>;  


      }  


      // ...

