##  Go full-stack  
with a framework

React is a library. It lets you put components together, but it doesn’t
prescribe how to do routing and data fetching. To build an entire app with
React, we recommend a full-stack React framework like [ Next.js
](https://nextjs.org) or  [ Remix ](https://remix.run) .

